<h2 id="conflict-resolution" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#conflict-resolution"><span>Conflict Resolution</span></a></h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Origin precedence</p>
<ul>
<li>when in conflict: <strong>Last Declaration Wins</strong></li>
<li>when not in conflict: <strong>Declarations Merge</strong></li>
</ul>
</li>
